Enrico Smith's body was discovered earlier this week. His car has been stolen. CAPE TOWN - No arrests have been made yet after a man's body was found at his Pelican Park house.Enrico Smith's body was discovered earlier this week. His car has been stolen.The police's Noloyiso Rwexana says: The circumstances surrounding this incident are under investigation. No one has been arrested at this stage. We urge the public to contact Crime Stop if they have any information at 08600 10111. 